ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
SubjectOrder Adding Toxic Substances to Schedule 1 to the Canadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
PrecisOrder ADDING TOXIC SUBSTANCES TO SCHEDULE 1 TO THE CANADIAN ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION ACT, 1999 in order to add DEHA, PREPOD and Solvent Red 23 to the Schedule which would enable the Government to implement regulatory instruments under the statutory authority of Canadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999 if such actions are deemed necessary.
